{"tid":21524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"燒生預測曾俊華做特首","createTime":"2016-12-04T02:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T14:30:19.000Z","uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f7055cd756398cb80d9bc5a09b9a7a4d0df26ab","tid":21524,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:03:26.000Z","msg":"財爺曾俊華周六出席電台節目時戴上一條綠呔，加上早前葉劉淑儀的「綠燈論」，引來各方猜測財爺勢必「去馬」參選特首。時事評論員蕭若元（蕭生）同日亦發表評論，在其Youtube頻道「蕭若元：最新蕭析」欄目上載題目為「特首選舉 曾俊華上馬！」片段，惟因蕭生亦有「燈神」稱號，例如早前預測美國總統選舉中特朗普將會慘敗，因此其評論一出，有網民擔心曾俊華會被「燈死」，紛紛希望蕭生可以預測梁振英連任，同時希望他不要預測財爺選情，驚呼「ABC頭號敵人，燒山！」<br />\n<br />\n蕭生在片中分析，曾俊華的表現等於承認會參選，態度就如「你爆我黑幕都唔驚」、「要同你死過」，並再次表示所有證據都證明今次北京不會欽點任何人，只會讓合資格人士參選，而若非有權威人士告知財爺可去馬，財爺斷不會「去馬」參選。他又指，若梁振英爭取連任，政務司司長林鄭月娥就絕對不會參選，因她不會「謀朝篡位」，但現時又有聲音指林鄭月娥或參選，因此梁振英或不會爭取連任，而現時中央的態度是要待選委會選舉結束後才准宣佈參選，現階段令梁振英非常難取得提名票。<br />\n<br />\n蕭生的「往績」不時為網民津津樂道，有網民曾列出蕭生早前、港大退聯失敗、雨傘運動後2年內無大型群眾運動、本民前梁天琦補選得3,000票、英國留歐等等，全部無一倖免估錯，有人笑言「次次都錯呢啲係實力」、「世界級燈神」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161204&amp;guid=56000585&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161204%26guid%3D56000585%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=4a683417\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161204%26guid%3D56000585%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=8e390d52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161204&amp;guid=56000585&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"fa39a6fe6d668cecfa12efe2aac8cce90ccb24ff","tid":21524,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:10:30.000Z","msg":"薯片叔叔咁就比人燈死左 rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54225bb34eeb9c0b1ec455498f91d8a309ed4b5","tid":21524,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>薯片叔叔咁就比人燈死左 rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n689俾左幾多錢燒山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec21fa685924c898caef55f9957ae3bdf66bc05","tid":21524,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:16:41.000Z","msg":"燈死"},{"pid":"6ed1012245bf55c4f6c04005fc9cb97e82979229","tid":21524,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:16:55.000Z","msg":"燈死"},{"pid":"b4a8591f153caec886aef9ba66d647b8b10f0889","tid":21524,"uid":3936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:18:53.000Z","msg":"品客bye <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca348f97b08a8b89c4540654a4e9c99e62582a6","tid":21524,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:20:46.000Z","msg":"死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4dd53f2beada3c959fe87468855e3eb5795db9","tid":21524,"uid":21122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:22:55.000Z","msg":"GG<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091f88e7b569f841b2d5cac37be79df0ca15a013","tid":21524,"uid":28437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:23:38.000Z","msg":"又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6caa0c7060bf408e91992986b00b3637c37519","tid":21524,"uid":26610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4338cc67a1d6eb3fa6d8bfcb329923ccf26ab52f","tid":21524,"uid":2857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:28:48.000Z","msg":"品客RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/by